title: Bug 130068[Regression]Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
description:
Description: Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with parameters.

Steps to reproduce: Follow the steps below to reproduce the issue.

1. Open the report that contains parameters.
2. Preview the report.

Observed Behavior (OB): The Report Parameter window does not pop up when previewing a report with parameters.

Expected Behavior (EB): The Report Parameter window should pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
OB: The Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
EB: The Report Parameter window should pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
